                        "en": {
                            "text": "<h3>IT Application Engineer</h3><p style='margin-bottom:15px;'>[[Experienced in developing enterprise applications, including {{RPA (Robotic Process Automation)}} solutions and {{Power Apps}} applications]]</p><h3>Professional Summary</h3><ul><li>A goal-oriented IT engineer with 5 years of experience in [[PM / Sales]] roles, with strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Hands-on experience in {{OEM manufacturing}} environments, collaborating across cultures and cross-functional teams.</li><li>Demonstrates solid {{communication}} and {{coordination}} skills, and able to work effectively in diverse team settings.</li></ul>"
                        },
                        "zh": {
                            "text": "<h3>IT應用系統工程師</h3><p style='margin-bottom:15px;'><strong>累積多個{{自動化流程 (RPA)}}、{{Power Apps}}企業應用程式等等之開發經驗</strong></p><h3>專業摘要</h3><ul><li>一位目標導向的IT 工程師，具備 5 年 [[專案管理/業務]] 的人際溝通與軟實力。</li><li>在{{OEM 工廠}}中擁有豐富的跨文化與跨部門協作經驗。</li><li>具備 {{良好的溝通能力}} 與 {{協調能力}}，能在多元團隊中有效合作。</li></ul>"
                        }
